IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. OCCURSNUM.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 ITEMS PIC 9(4) OCCURS 3 TIMES.
01 IDX PIC 9(4) VALUE 2.
01 TOTAL PIC 9(5) VALUE 0.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PARA.
    MOVE 3 TO ITEMS(1)
    MOVE 4 TO ITEMS(IDX)
    MOVE 5 TO ITEMS(3)
    COMPUTE TOTAL = ITEMS(1) + ITEMS(IDX) + ITEMS(3)
    DISPLAY "TOTAL " TOTAL
    STOP RUN.
